name: Holy Mountain Pentagram Sticker
description:
We had some little vinyl stickers made up of the sneaky little Pentagram that popped up on wolf T shirt design last year. 

They measure just under 7cms and are printed in a lovely grey colour. 

They are vinyl cut out stickers so are super durable so you can stick them practically anywhere. 

Limited number will not be reprinted in this colour again. 

We post out UK First Class twice a week.

name: Caduceus Tee
description:
The Caduceus was a staff carried by Hermes who in ancient Greece was the dude who guided people round the under world. However his staff didn't have a skull on the body of snake. So make of that what you will.

Website printed on reverse

Designed by Craig Robson. 
Printed on B&C Exact 150.
